title: Negotiations
author: chrisseb
pages:
#- Hello, people of Terminus. I Chrisseb, a writing this to inform you that I have taken this railroad to this side of the line & will be tunneling upwards. From the surface I will walk a distance & start a small outpost to collect iron. I will be depositing
#- 20% of my findings in this chest in my way back through as compensation. I would like to assure you that I will not be divulging your rails location to anyone. 
#- 